  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A minor mesh-topology correction was applied in the model revision of 2025-11-10; the rheology boundary-condition dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-17) predates that revision. The assessment team judged the revision not material to the dataset's applicability without performing a formal re-validation sweep, introducing a stale-input epistemic gap (W-EP-03).",
