      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ initiated but input probability distributions for blood viscosity and hemolysis model coefficients drawn from the rheology boundary-condition dataset (dataVintage 2025-10-17), which predates the model revision of 2025-11-10. The revision introduced a corrected impeller tip-clearance geometry; the assessment team noted this change was 'not material' to rheological inputs and retained the pre-revision dataset without re-running the characterization experiments. No formal re-validation of input relevance post-revision was performed. Achieved level 2 against required level 4.",
